-- Satellite Monitoring Application
    This Node.js application monitors the status of a satellite using real-time altitude data from the Carsfast API. It exposes two API endpoints: /stats and /health.

Prerequisites
Node.js installed on your machine
npm (Node Package Manager) installed on your machine

-- Run
    1. Clone the repository to your local machine
        - git clone
    2. Navigate to the project directory
    3. Install dependencies
        - npm install
    4. Start the server
        1. src/app.js
        2. Access API Endpoints
           Stats Example: curl http://localhost:3000/stats
           Health Example: curl http://localhost:3000/health
-- Unit Test
    npm test